    "body": "Those exceptions are not errors: Errors are stuff displayed to the use while the exceptions listed above are just exceptional terminations of some compiler routines, which could result in displaying an error to the user but does not have to.\r\n\r\nApart from that, the Error class should not be an exception, because it should not be thrown, it should just be added to the list of errors.",
